  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine if there is a difference between wireless ECG and wired ECG findings.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to compare ECG recordings from the Signalife Fidelity 100 Wireless
      12-lead ECG Monitor System to that of the GE 5000 Wired 12-lead ECG Monitor System during
      rest and while walking. We hypothesize that ECG recordings from the wireless system will be
      equivalent to recordings from the standard wired system.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
